 style=\"font-size: x-large;\">另外好重要好重要好重要</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aoLoCBH.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaoLoCBH.png&h=99a60b07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ynKAtJo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FynKAtJo.png&h=73eded90&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b8d0bb99bd64c8a3f0af3157639b4e34720adb7a","tid":1530033,"uid":296618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T01:20:32.000Z","msg":"聽日繼續 推"},{"pid":"b95efa9da7f6b2d7a90ada0f33cd894640415eec","tid":1530033,"uid":55544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T01:21:43.000Z","msg":"（集中）92集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530114\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530114</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n今日係有集會，仲有不反對通知書"},{"pid":"a5d3d9fa17d0bed72e309a013d7590828ffbc4bd","tid":1530033,"uid":31215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85cbc3d02da574c167b67a2bd38d6d15b5b69321","tid":1530033,"uid":108347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T01:15:28.000Z","msg":"唔關宣傳事，係香港嘅勇武派屬少數，和理非低風險可以好容易動員，你睇人鏈都咁多人<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">但係一有後果就只會得噃勇武敢做</span>，如果有十萬勇武黑警收咗皮啦<br />\n<br />\n其實冇需要再分化，繼續和理非拖仲好，到佢開槍威脅到自己啲人先會勇武"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T01:22:22.000Z","msg":"個當然cost越大越少人<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以之後諗活動<br />\n一定要計算埋cost<br />\n你要人多，個cost就要低<br />\n想搞高風險行動，人數就一定少<br />\n大家都要接受呢個現實<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dcea94a752b9eba001c2da7773baff4945435de","tid":1530033,"uid":22700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6560ec0131928863e1dd2842f7926cb3ce13001e","tid":1530033,"uid":31215,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"cde634aa31df046328a8a5a8d0a1463cc021c073","tid":1530033,"uid":204309,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09